<emphasis id="ED7980F65614659F835291474B266E3F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Phorocardius florentini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Fleutiaux, 1895). 
<emphasis id="0CDBF7F504C304499BDFC73B694436C2" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">A</emphasis>
male habitus, dorsal view 
