female habitus, lateral view 
<emphasis id="98A77D2163EA60643239A899608B2106" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">E</emphasis>
aedeagus, ventral view, arrow indicating preapical lateral expansion 
<emphasis id="4FB71885E27524F16E28CEB37B8DD1DD" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">F</emphasis>
aedeagus, dorsal view, arrow indicating preapical lateral expansion 
<emphasis id="1C577E7FDB49C2CE11DE005AEC198DBF" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">G</emphasis>
